<L>__{exterior military courtyard cuxhaven day}
<A>__{the cuxhaven troops are drawn up to receive a new regiment, arrived from england. roderick sees, marching at the head of his company, his old friend, captain grogan, who gives him a wink.}
<C>__{roderick }
<D>__{six weeks after we arrived in cuxhaven, we were reinforced by gales regiment of foot from england, and i promise you the sight of grogan's face was most welcome to me, for it assured me that a friend was near me.}
